{"tid":1211624,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[爆卦] 香港警察所用的武器","createTime":"2019-06-12T16:09:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T06:35:57.000Z","uid":78913,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9a0fcfbbb565a432465e429e31f01392a0ab3d7d","tid":1211624,"uid":78913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T16:09:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://disp.cc/m/163-bsav\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdisp.cc%2Fm%2F163-bsav&d=o1jNmZJj5m3DpFdm5BDgv%2FYtrFBHe52Fn%2F6n3rMGN5k%3D&h=cd8bd841\" target=\"_blank\">https://disp.cc/m/163-bsav</a><br />\n<br />\n現在人在國外 聽朋友說香港出事了<br />\n從水管看直播 發現香港警察這次用的武器<br />\n真的比台灣的鎮暴警察厲害多了<br />\n<br />\n除了基本的盾牌棍棒之外<br />\n香港警察出動了多種槍枝來對付民眾<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（一）催淚彈<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/QiEcV6U.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FQiEcV6U.gif&h=55a616b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（二）鎮暴槍<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ZgRReZ5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FZgRReZ5.png&h=8c2bd325&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/FCBpudV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FFCBpudV.png&h=fe7ab91d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n較少會被注意到 但短小靈活<br />\n算是漆彈槍射出實心塑膠彈<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/q00cYXd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fq00cYXd.jpg&h=ef2b7604&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港警察從側翼攻擊移動中的民眾<br />\n<br />\n（三）橡膠彈<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/vbDXhGF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FvbDXhGF.jpg&h=802c29a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n利用火藥給予的強大動能 推動橡膠彈<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/tT2COUL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FtT2COUL.png&h=4394deec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/3ChlIu8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F3ChlIu8.jpg&h=b7d48fb3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n可在盾牌後面支援<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/gjA5eKR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FgjA5eKR.jpg&h=c94acc8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n或是協助攻擊指定目標<br />\n<br />\n有人在地上發現用過的彈殼<br />\n使用的彈藥為 ALS 1202<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/XWU9WE3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FXWU9WE3.jpg&h=c9dcdc68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/znpcQlf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FznpcQlf.jpg&h=4133178f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n是一種帶有穩定翼的橡膠彈<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Fj1YKbf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FFj1YKbf.png&h=e479822a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n注意左下說明<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins><strong>Serious injury or death may occur if the product is<br />\nmisused or in rare or unexpected instances.<br />\n<br />\n在近距離內發射將導致嚴重傷害或死亡</strong></ins></span></span><br />\n<br />\n因為該彈藥為<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><em><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">低致死（Less-Lethal）</span></em></strong></span><br />\n而不是非至死（Non-Lethal）<br />\n<br />\n被擊中的部位很嚴重 組織被破壞 肉會凹進去<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/giITtDw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FgiITtDw.jpg&h=4595d670&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/NdHn6SM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FNdHn6SM.jpg&h=7608d9f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/UkdHtrx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FUkdHtrx.jpg&h=c908c4cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n民眾想要用雨傘擋住火藥打過來的橡膠彈<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/vbDXhGF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FvbDXhGF.jpg&h=802c29a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/nP3AA3h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FnP3AA3h.jpg&h=c5700b0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一發馬上就退散了<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因為天氣熱 香港的民眾大多數完全沒有任何保護<br />\n受傷的人數應該還會持續增加<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今日香港，＿＿＿＿。"},{"pid":"198c6ec506c055907d6b9df08d5299598d824d6a","tid":1211624,"uid":48947,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9a0fcfbbb565a432465e429e31f01392a0ab3d7d","tid":1211624,"uid":78913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T16:09:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://disp.cc/m/163-bsav\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdisp.cc%2Fm%2F163-bsav&d=o1jNmZJj5m3DpFdm5BDgv%2FYtrFBHe52Fn%2F6n3rMGN5k%3D&h=cd8bd841\" target=\"_blank\">https://disp.cc/m/163-bsav</a><br />\n<br />\n現在人在國外 聽朋友說香港出事了<br />\n從水管看直播 發現香港警察這次用的武器<br />\n真的比台灣的鎮暴警察厲害多了<br />\n<br />\n除了基本的盾牌棍棒之外<br />\n香港警察出動了多種槍枝來對付民眾<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（一）催淚彈<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/QiEcV6U.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FQiEcV6U.gif&h=55a616b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（二）鎮暴槍<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ZgRReZ5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FZgRReZ5.png&h=8c2bd325&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/FCBpudV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FFCBpudV.png&h=fe7ab91d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n較少會被注意到 但短小靈活<br />\n算是漆彈槍射出實心塑膠彈<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/q00cYXd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fq00cYXd.jpg&h=ef2b7604&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港警察從側翼攻擊移動中的民眾<br />\n<br />\n（三）橡膠彈<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/vbDXhGF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FvbDXhGF.jpg&h=802